General Instructions:
	- Follow the instructions stated in the INSTALL.TXT to download the program.
	- To run the program go into the "bin/" directory and type ./Poker to execute the chess program.
	- After executing ./Poker use the GUI interface to use the program.
	- Press Play to connect to the Poker Server.
	- Once all players have connected press play and the users will be moved to the Poker table
	- The player will be prompted with Raise, Fold, or Call on their turn
	- During the Preflop, Flop, Turn, and river cards will be dealt 

Extra Features:
	- Client and Server Systems
	- Playable Bots
	- Hand Percentages
	- Bot levels

